<p><a href="/scp-cn-595">SCP-CN-595</a> 失控的五</p>
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">+&nbsp;解說</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
